com.fasterxml.jackson.core

Class TSFBuilder<F extends JsonFactory,B extends TSFBuilder<F,B>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.core.TSFBuilder<F,B>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonFactoryBuilder

    public abstract class TSFBuilder<F extends JsonFactory,B extends TSFBuilder<F,B>>
extends Object
    Since 2.10, Builder class is offered for creating token stream factories with difference configurations: with 3.x they will be fully immutable.
    Since:
    2.10
